	        	<h1>Where can I find open data?</h1>
	<br/><br/>
				<p>
				
<a href="http://publicdata.eu/">PublicData.eu</a> contains numerous datasets from public bodies across Europe - including from <a href="http://lod2.okfn.org/eu-data-catalogues/">many of these catalogues</a>.			</p>
			<p>
If you would like to suggest a dataset or a collection of datasets for people to use please <a ref="http://ckan.net/package/new">register it on CKAN</a>, making sure to add the tag <a href="http://ckan.net/tag/?q=opendatachallenge">'opendatachallenge'</a>.</p>

<p>If you run a local, regional or national data catalogue and you would like to have your open datasets included on publicdata.eu, please <a href="mailto:info@okfn.org">please drop us a line</a>!</p>
			</p>
			
